    <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl pb-2"> ❓ Who is Henventory for?</h2>
    <div class="pl-10">
      <p class="pb-2"><b>Henventory</b> helps chicken farmers keep track of egg production.</p>
      <p class="pb-2">Whether you have a small backyard flock or several dozen hens, Henventory will answer questions like:</p>
      <ul class="font-semibold italic text-sm">
        <li class="py-1">🥚 How many eggs do I get per day, on average? </li>
